的房贷，生活的开销，孩子的开销，这一笔笔算下来，睁眼就欠几千块 中午点了一杯伯牙绝弦，确实很好喝，但是好贵～化妆品也好久没买了，不是不想化妆不想收拾，实在是干完活也没什么时间和心情收拾自己了～ 在北京奋斗这么久了，就是知道这里比老家更好，希望孩子的起点在这，不用再自己去淌 10 年换来跟我一样的想法～ 希望能越来越好吧～睡不着觉，继续干点活，希望明天能从自习室早点走，省一个小时的费用"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-19a2d09d7aac4ce255a591c2b0c4c4c9_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657489982"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8It4afi5CSi/ENEAMaCTEwODM4NjY1OSDQjdiyBjAAODNAL3IJNjU3NDg5OTgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1717179885.739153", "card_id": "Q_656343425", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 94}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "旅游和存钱哪一个更重要？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "年轻不旅游，老了就走不动了，也没有那么多精力；可是现在存钱等老了就有时间去享受生活了。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656343425"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8It4afi5CSi/ENEAMaCTEwODEzMTg1NSC/gZ6yBjAAOHdAMHIJNjU2MzQzNDI1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1717179885.739459", "card_id": "Q_651021172", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 10}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么需要 RLHF？SFT 不够吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "RLHF 对于大模型微调是必要的吗？为什么？为啥 chatgpt 和 instructgpt 在 SFT 以后仍使用了 RLHF？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7886389f278e4b10529f73e0203a699e_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/651021172"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIt4afi5CSi/ENEAMa